      "home.hero1.title": "HAPPY WINTER",
      "home.hero1.subtitle": "FROM FLORENCE",
      "home.hero2.title": "WHEN TIME <br>BECOMES ART",
      "home.hero2.desc": "Da Vinci was born from a dream: to unite art and watchmaking to create timepieces that blend beauty and precision.",
      "home.hero3.title": "THE STARRY NIGHT <br>THE WINDOW TO THE STARS",
      "home.hero3.desc": "Inspired by the sky Van Gogh contemplated from his room, The Starry Night captures the poetry of a vibrant, luminous night. A watch that lets art shine on your wrist.",
      "home.section1.title": "EVERY INSTANT <br>BECOMES A CANVAS <br>TO CONTEMPLATE",
      "home.section1.desc": "Step into the Da Vinci universe<BR>Discover a world where each creation draws inspiration from the masters of art <BR>and their timeless emotions. From Monet‚Äôs luminous softness<BR> to Picasso‚Äôs expressive power, our collections pay tribute <BR>to the works that shaped history.<BR><BR>\n\nEach watch captures a unique atmosphere, an artistic vision, <BR>a subtle movement like a fragment of art worn on the wrist.<BR> Explore our collections and let yourself be drawn by the poetry of colors,<BR> the strength of forms, and the beauty of details.",
      "home.monet.caption": "La Promenade watch <br>Light captured on the wrist <br><br>Born from a breath of wind and a moving sky,\nLa Promenade paints time with Monet‚Äôs softness.\nEach second becomes a caress of light,\nan invitation to walk in the eternity of colors.",
      "home.picasso.caption": "Guernica watch <br>The brilliance of chaos sculpted in time <br><br>Born from a fragment of revolt and beauty,\nthe Guernica watch captures the cubist soul in motion.\nIts fractured lines intertwine with the silence of metal,\nmaking every second vibrate\nlike a heartbeat of art and freedom.",
      "home.hero4.title": "THE CHRONOSPHERE <br>THE HOUR OF WONDERS",
      "home.hero4.desc": "This watch, inspired by the universe of Nivins McTwisp, <br>is not contemplated like a painting,<br>\nbut it remains a work of art in its own right.<br>\nCome closer‚Ä¶ and be surprised<br>by a creation where art is not painted: it is told.",
      "home.services.title": "DISCOVER DA VINCI SERVICES",
      "home.services.desc": "At Da Vinci, we offer far more than luxury watches: we deliver a unique, personalized experience for every watch enthusiast. Our services are designed to elevate the encounter between art and time, while providing a bespoke level of care.<BR><BR>\n\nAppointments to discover our collections\nStep into the Da Vinci world by booking an appointment in one of our boutiques or exclusive ateliers. Our experts guide you through our luxury collections, present iconic models, and help you choose the piece that best reflects your style and tastes. Each appointment is designed as a private visit where art and watchmaking meet in an elegant, inspiring setting.<BR><BR>\n\nAppointments for watch care<BR>\nYour Da Vinci watch deserves careful attention to ensure durability and performance. With our maintenance and service appointment program, our specialized watchmakers care for every detail of your timepiece. Whether it‚Äôs a mechanical adjustment, a complete overhaul, or a specific repair, we provide precise follow‚Äëup and quality service faithful to Da Vinci excellence.",
      "home.service1.caption": "BOOK AN APPOINTMENT <br><br> Come discover our creations in person and let every moment tell our watchmaking expertise",
      "home.service2.caption": "ENTER <br>OUR MASTERPIECES<br><br>Ensure the longevity and precision of your watch thanks to our dedicated after‚Äësales service",
      "home.boutique.title": "FIND <br>YOUR BOUTIQUE",
      "home.boutique.desc": "Step into a universe where time meets art. <br><br>Our boutiques, designed like true watch galleries, invite you to discover each creation from a unique perspective, guided by advisors dedicated to experience and emotion.",
      "home.newsletter.left": "RECEIVE OUR <br>LATEST CREATIONS",
      "home.newsletter.right": "News, new releases <br>and watchmaking inspirations",
      "home.cookie.title": "Respect for your privacy is our priority",
      "home.cookie.text": "We and our partners store and/or access information on a device, such as cookies, and process personal data such as unique identifiers and standard information sent by a device for personalized advertising and content, ad and content measurement, audience insights, and service development.",

