      "histoire.title": "DA VINCI",
      "histoire.hero.desc": "Our brand was born from a dream‚Ä¶",
      "histoire.hero.cta": "Learn more",
      "histoire.section1.title": "Where Time <br>and Art Were Born",
      "histoire.section2.title": "The Visionary Who <br>Saw More Than Time",
      "histoire.section3.title": "The Birth <br>of a Legacy",
      "histoire.section4.title": "Three Centuries of Craft, One Unchanged Soul",
      "histoire.section5.title": "A Sensory Journey <br>Between Painting and Watchmaking",
      "histoire.section6.title": "Enter the Da Vinci <br>Universe",
      "histoire.section1.text": "Florence, 1674. A workshop, a glint, the scent of oil and wood.<BR>The Da Vinci idea is born: to join the painter‚Äôs hand with mechanical rigor.<BR>Each watch becomes an intimate canvas, laid upon time.<BR>Poetry guides the gesture, precision keeps the pulse.<BR>A humble origin, a luminous ambition.<BR>And art begins to beat.",
      "histoire.section2.text": "Lorenzo Da Verdi reads light as the language of time.<BR>He travels, observes, assembles: painting and watchmaking speak with one voice.<BR>‚ÄúIf the brush captures the instant, a watch can preserve its soul.‚Äù<BR>In 1683 he opens a workshop where artists and watchmakers create together.<BR>The first pieces are gifts, offered like promises.<BR>A tradition is born, alive and transmissible.",
      "histoire.section3.text": "The house crosses centuries, from baroque to mechanical revolutions.<BR>Its tools evolve, never its soul.<BR>In the 19th century, Da Vinci Arte & Tempo affirms its name and vision.<BR>Engraving, painted dials, patient hands: the ritual endures.<BR>Each generation guards yesterday‚Äôs hand and tomorrow‚Äôs impulse.<BR>An inheritance that does not fade.",
      "histoire.section4.text": "Da Vinci remains faithful to its original vision.<BR>The world changes; authenticity stays.<BR>Each collection is conceived as a living gallery.<BR>Artists, historians, and watchmakers meet there.<BR>Technique serves emotion, creation serves time.<BR>And every watch tells a singular story.",
      "histoire.section5.text": "Here, color becomes a dial, texture becomes an engraving.<BR>Museum light glides across polished steel.<BR>Each page invites you to feel before you understand.<BR>The artistic gesture converses with horological precision.<BR>You no longer watch time: you listen to it.<BR>And matter tells what it knows.",
      "histoire.section6.text": "Step into our boutiques and let the silence speak.<BR>Art meets time; heritage comes alive.<BR>Each piece reveals itself at your rhythm.<BR>Materials narrate, light underlines.<BR>You do not visit: you feel.<BR>And the Da Vinci universe welcomes you.",
      "histoire.boutiques": "OUR BOUTIQUES",

