      "product.guarantee.title": "International warranty <BR>Da Vinci <BR>Quality and reliability assured",
      "product.guarantee.desc": "International 2‚Äëyear warranty, extendable to 5 years at authorized retailers.<BR>A clear promise, set like a signature.<BR>Precise checks, meticulous assembly.<BR>Technique protects the poetry of time.<BR>Each watch moves calmly through the everyday.<BR>Quiet confidence on the wrist.",
      "product.discover.more": "Discover pieces that may enchant you ‚Äì Da Vinci luxury watches",
      "product.discover.desc": "A selection where art meets precision.<BR>Sculpted lines, dials that breathe.<BR>Light traces a discreet path.<BR>Craft becomes a story.<BR>Follow form, material, detail.<BR>Choose the emotion that suits you.",
      "product.universe.title": "Enter the Da Vinci <br>Universe",
      "product.universe.desc": "Step into our boutiques, where time becomes art.<BR>A place of light, silence and matter.<BR>Each piece reveals itself gently.<BR>Technique steps back, poetry remains.<BR>You touch, you observe, you feel.<BR>And the watchmaker‚Äôs gesture finds its meaning.",
      "product.universe.cta": "OUR BOUTIQUES",

      "monet.title": "DA VINCI",
      "monet.hero.title": "LA PROMENADE <br>LIGHT CAPTURED ON THE WRIST",
      "monet.hero.desc": "Timeless elegance and watchmaking art<BR>Inspired by Monet, La Promenade captures moving light.<BR>A dial like a soft landscape.<BR>Clean lines, a light presence.<BR>Precision stays quiet, never loud.<BR>A watch that breathes on the wrist.",
      "monet.section.box.title": "THE CASE",
      "monet.section.box.desc": "Case with pure lines, satin finishes, a fine glow.<BR>The diameter remains balanced and calm.<BR>Light glides without harsh edges.<BR>Contemporary steel, carefully worked.<BR>The structure is light, the fit secure.<BR>Elegance in controlled restraint.",
      "monet.section.dial.title": "THE DIAL",
      "monet.section.dial.desc": "Impressionist dial, blue nuances, gentle depth.<BR>Matter suggests movement.<BR>Fine indexes keep legibility clear.<BR>Hands brush the light.<BR>Poetry remains, precision leads.<BR>A miniature painting for time.",
      "monet.section.bracelet.title": "THE BRACELET",
      "monet.section.bracelet.desc": "Integrated bracelet, fluid links, soft fall.<BR>The line of the case continues.<BR>Each joint stays precise and supple.<BR>Comfort disappears, form remains.<BR>A continuous design without breaks.<BR>The silhouette closes in quiet.",
      "monet.section.calibre.title": "AURORA 01: <br>PRECISION <br>BORN OF INNOVATION",
      "monet.section.calibre.desc": "Aurora 01, automatic movement with 44 jewels.<BR>379 components, rigorously adjusted.<BR>3 Hz cadence, stable and calm.<BR>72‚Äëhour power reserve.<BR>Visible through sapphire caseback.<BR>Technique becomes signature.",

      "picasso.title": "DA VINCI",
      "picasso.hero.title": "GUERNICA <br>THE SPARK OF CHAOS",
      "picasso.hero.desc": "Refined design and contemporary watchmaking<BR>Guernica speaks in clear graphics and tension.<BR>Geometry captures light and shadow.<BR>Clean lines, architectural presence.<BR>Material stays sober, impact strong.<BR>Modern balance without compromise.",
      "picasso.section.box.title": "THE CASE",
      "picasso.section.box.desc": "Architectural case, controlled edges.<BR>Satin surfaces, measured reflections.<BR>The form feels modern and firm.<BR>Volume remains precise, never heavy.<BR>A silhouette drawn with rigor.<BR>Design speaks before time begins.",
      "picasso.section.dial.title": "THE DIAL",
      "picasso.section.dial.desc": "Faceted texture, deep reflections, graphic precision.<BR>Light changes, the dial responds.<BR>Sculpted indexes stay clearly readable.<BR>A discreet counter structures the whole.<BR>Decor becomes rhythm, the hour stays calm.<BR>Geometry in service of time.",
      "picasso.section.bracelet.title": "THE BRACELET",
      "picasso.section.bracelet.desc": "Integrated bracelet, contrasted finishes, clean profile.<BR>Each link extends the geometry.<BR>Comfort stays fluid, hold remains stable.<BR>Continuity to the wrist.<BR>Robustness lives in the detail.<BR>A contemporary, precise gesture.",
      "picasso.section.calibre.title": "OBSCURA 02 CALIBRE: THE ARCHITECTURE OF TIME",
      "picasso.section.calibre.desc": "Obscura 02, automatic with 32 jewels.<BR>278 components, cleanly assembled.<BR>3 Hz frequency, steady running.<BR>65‚Äëhour power reserve.<BR>Visible through sapphire caseback, structured mechanics.<BR>Technique becomes architecture.",

      "vangogh.title": "DA VINCI",
      "vangogh.hero.title": "THE STARRY NIGHT <br>THE WINDOW TO THE STARS",
      "vangogh.hero.desc": "Fusion of art and haute horlogerie<BR>Starry Night on the wrist, deep blues in motion.<BR>The dial breathes like a living canvas.<BR>Polished case lets light sing.<BR>Hands remain quiet, poetry remains.<BR>Time becomes landscape.",
      "vangogh.section.box.title": "THE CASE",
      "vangogh.section.box.desc": "Round polished case, timeless elegance.<BR>Harmonious proportions, calm sheen.<BR>Light glides over soft curves.<BR>A refined presence without excess.<BR>Tradition meets modernity.<BR>A quiet frame for light.",
      "vangogh.section.dial.title": "THE DIAL",
      "vangogh.section.dial.desc": "Inspired dial, deep blues, swirling movement.<BR>Nuances vibrate without hiding the hour.<BR>Fine indexes, clear reading.<BR>Hands skim the light.<BR>Emotion leads, precision reassures.<BR>A miniature painting in balance.",
      "vangogh.section.bracelet.title": "THE BRACELET",
      "vangogh.section.bracelet.desc": "Textured leather, supple, tone‚Äëon‚Äëtone with the dial.<BR>The wrist finds material and calm.<BR>Comfort settles, the line stays pure.<BR>Careful finish, secure hold.<BR>No break, only continuity.<BR>The work wears with simplicity.",
      "vangogh.section.calibre.title": "NOCTURNA 1903 CALIBRE: <br>THE MOVEMENT <br>OF STARRY NIGHTS",
      "vangogh.section.calibre.desc": "Nocturna 1903, automatic with 38 jewels.<BR>312 components, finely adjusted.<BR>4 Hz frequency, stable precision.<BR>70‚Äëhour power reserve.<BR>Visible mechanics, discreet and sure.<BR>The beat becomes a silent song.",

      "lapin.title": "DA VINCI",
      "lapin.hero.title": "THE CHRONOSPHERE <br>THE HOUR OF WONDERS",
      "lapin.hero.desc": "Heritage and refinement<BR>Chronosph√®re revives the elegance of another era.<BR>Delicate engravings, Roman dial, noble chain.<BR>Opening becomes ritual.<BR>Precision lives in the detail.<BR>A collector‚Äôs piece with intact charm.",
      "lapin.section.box.title": "THE CASE",
      "lapin.section.box.desc": "Engraved case, hinged cover, ceremonial gesture.<BR>The surface tells the craftsman‚Äôs work.<BR>The dial reveals itself in calm.<BR>Heritage character, consciously worn.<BR>Tradition rests in the hand.<BR>Elegance that crosses time.",
      "lapin.section.dial.title": "THE DIAL",
      "lapin.section.dial.desc": "Roman numerals, fine hands, small seconds.<BR>Clear reading, classic rhythm.<BR>The dial breathes old‚Äëworld watchmaking.<BR>Each marker is made to last.<BR>Precision serves simplicity.<BR>A serene, timeless face.",
      "lapin.section.bracelet.title": "THE CHAIN",
      "lapin.section.bracelet.desc": "Wide‚Äëlink chain, robust and elegant.<BR>Each link secures the fit.<BR>A noble accessory, built to last.<BR>The wear stays secure, the line stays beautiful.<BR>The chain becomes a signature.<BR>A detail that tells the era.",
      "lapin.section.calibre.title": "HERITAGE 1820 CALIBRE: <br>ANCESTRAL PRECISION",
      "lapin.section.calibre.desc": "H√©ritage 1820, manual with 17 jewels.<BR>156 components, precisely assembled.<BR>2.5 Hz frequency, steady running.<BR>48‚Äëhour power reserve.<BR>Mechanics honor tradition.<BR>Time advances with measure.",

      "shop.paris.name": "DA VINCI PARIS",
