      "collections.desc": "At <strong>DA VINCI</strong>, every luxury watch is a true <strong>work of watchmaking art</strong>. Born from the meeting of <strong>artistic creation</strong> and <strong>horological precision</strong>, our collection pays tribute to the greatest masters and the timeless emotions they captured.<br><br>\n        \n        Each piece is conceived like a painting to wear on the wrist: lines inspired by art history, details crafted with rigor, and a mechanism in which <strong>time becomes expression</strong>. Our watches do more than tell time: they tell a story, translate a vision, and celebrate the perfect alliance between <strong>art, watch design, and timeless elegance</strong>.<br><br>\n        \n        Explore the <strong>DA VINCI</strong> universe and discover time differently through prestige watches that embody <strong>artisanal excellence</strong>, <strong>refined design</strong>, and <strong>luxury haute horlogerie</strong>. Each creation is designed for those who seek beauty, precision, and emotion in every second.",
      "cookies.h1": "Cookie Policy",
      "cookies.section1": "<h2>1. Personal data collected</h2>\n    <p>A cookie is a small text file stored on your computer, smartphone, or other device (\"terminal\") when you visit a website.\nCookies allow a site to recognize your device and remember certain information, in particular to improve your user experience.\n\nDa Vinci uses cookies to:\n        <ul>\n            <li>ensure the proper functioning of the site,</li>\n            <li>improve navigation and user experience,</li>\n            <li>measure audience and performance,</li>\n            <li>offer tailored content and communications.</li>\n        </ul>\n    Cookies do not allow us to identify you directly by name, but they may be linked to personal data you have voluntarily provided via our services.\n    </p>",
      "cookies.section2": "<h2>2. TYPES OF COOKIES USED</h2>\n    <p>When you browse www.davinci-watches.com, different types of cookies may be placed.\n\n  Strictly necessary cookies\n\nThese cookies are essential for the site to function.\nThey allow in particular:</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>management of privacy preferences,</li>\n        <li>secure access to protected areas,</li>\n        <li>proper display of the site.</li>\n    </ul><br>\n    <p>‚û°Ô∏è They cannot be disabled.<br>\n‚öôÔ∏è Functional cookies<br><br>\n\nThese cookies improve site functionality and personalization (language, display preferences, etc.).<br><br>\n\nRefusing these cookies may limit certain features.<br>\nüìä Performance and analytics cookies<br><br>\n\nThese cookies help us understand how visitors use the site (pages visited, browsing time, possible errors).<br><br>\n\nCollected data is aggregated and anonymous and is used only to improve the site.<br>\nüéØ Targeting and advertising cookies<br><br>\n\nThese cookies may be used to display content or ads tailored to your interests, notably via third‚Äëparty platforms (social networks, marketing tools).<br><br>\n\nIf you refuse these cookies, you will still see content, but less personalized.<br>\nüåê Social media cookies<br><br>\n\nThese cookies enable the integration of sharing features via social networks (Instagram, LinkedIn, etc.).<br>\nThey may track your browsing on other sites.</p>",
