      "cookies.section4": "<h2>4. MANAGING YOUR PREFERENCES</h2>\n    <p>On your first visit, a cookie management banner allows you to:</p>\n        <ul>\n            <li>accept all cookies,</li>\n            <li>refuse certain cookies,</li>\n            <li>customize your preferences.</li>\n        </ul>\n    <p>You can change your choices at any time via the ‚ÄúCookie Settings‚Äù section of the site.</p>",
